	** Following is useful for hourly log purpose
	local datehour =ustrregexra(regexr("`c(current_date)'"," 20","") +"_"+regexr("`c(current_time)'",":[0-9]+:[0-9]+","")," ","") //saves string in 4Mar23_13 format, equivalent to 4th march 2023, 13 hour.
	
